Can play a card when it is the PLAY phase
When a card is played it enters the WAIT phase for 1 second then returns
  to the PLAY phase
There are seven colors, red, orange, yellow, green, blue, indigo, and violet
The player starts with one of each card

The cards:

Add a red and an orange token
Replace an orange token for the token of your choice
Remove all green tokens and add two yellow tokens
If there is an indigo token add a violet token
Add a green token
Remove two tokens of the same color to add a red, orange, blue, and indigo token